<p><strong>R.E.A.C.H.</strong></p>
<p>R.E.A.C.H. (Recreation Empowering Active Community Helpers) is a City of Ottawa initiative for youth in Kanata and West Carleton. Our goal is to provide a fun and welcoming environment for students to work towards and complete their 40-hours of community involvement while becoming active members of the community by planning and hosting events in the community.</p>
<p>For more information, visit <a href="https://youthconnexion2.wixsite.com/youthconnexion">Youth Connexion</a>.<br>
